Title: Grafana: Annotation queries were not applying host filter
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1589536522
Edition: cee
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

When using the annotations feature of our Grafana connector, the
explicit host filter provided by Grafana was not used correctly.
This made Checkmk respond with annotations to unrelated hosts.

The host regex filter was applied correctly
